BURI PLAC Laurens Co of S.C.

Gideon and Anne Coker Yeargin moved from Greenville Co. to Laurens Co.
Circa 1856. They built their home appr. one and a half miles north west of
Dial's Methodist Church about 100 yds. off Cooley Rd.in Dial's Township.
Their old homestead is still standing and in reasonably good shape. The
Cooley family has been living there for almost ninety years.
